basic.floral_language:
Zinnia angustifolia 
Floriography: warm-hearted, sunny, positive
Zinnia angustifolia will complete its life cycle in one year. Beautiful color. Flower shape is like a small sun, under sunlight, clustered lovely flowers especially dazzling and beautiful. In 2016, a Zinnia angustifolia at the International Space Station was the first flower that bloomed in the outer space.
Zinnia angustifolia likes sunny days, but avoid direct strong sunlight. Flowering from June to October for 3-4 weeks.
basic.blooming: Flowering period June-October, viewing period 3-4 weeks
basic.color: Flower color dark red, rose red, white, orange
